The Multimat Trekker Pillow is a very versatile item that will self-inflate to a 1.25 cushion, but can be further inflated with a couple of breathes, to form a pillow. Complete with Velcro joining strip, the hook side of which should be fixed to the top of your sleeping mattress, the self-inflating pillow can be fixed in place for sleeping, or packed for use in a day sack. The Trekker Mat has become the choice of many Military personnel because of its unique design and color combination that sets it apart from the competition. Self-Inflating Mats provide extra comfort sleeping on top of rocks and hard surfaces but also helps to add a barrier between you and the cold ground beneath. Super-fast valve giving 3x airflow for fast inflation/deflation. Mats supplied with microfiber-lined stuff sack/pillow case, retaining band and repair kit.Multimat Trekker Mat and Pillow Combo in Hunter Green

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
